Step 1 : Webserver 
- We need to configure webserver ANY (tomcat/nginx) on any Cloud distribution for Ex amazon EC2 or AZURES VM services
step 2 : configuring PHP-FPM , Redis , MYSql, Elastic search 
- need installation of  all this packeges also we have to setup different server for MySQL and chose the databases 
step 3 : security considerations
- need to set the proxy / firewalls for the nodes and servers.
step 4 : monitoring and scaling 
- we have to configure the tools like Grafana, nagios , ELK stack etc also for scaling we need configure more instances for tranffic management 
step 6 : backup & recovery
- need to take regular backups also we have to amke sure the version controlling for an application.

